documents.commentText:
To Whom It May Concern;
My daughter was diagnosed with Fibromyalgia after experiencing debilitating unexplained pain. The drugs that the doctors prescribed caused unacceptable side effects and did not do much to alleviate the pain.  The drugs also took away the ability to work full time.  Since she began using Kratom, she has had significant relief from the debilitating pain. She is also working full time.
Thank You for Listening,
